API for working with touch screens

add(x, y, width, height, data) -- Adds a hit area
hitTest(x, y)          -- Hit tests a position
clear()                -- Clears all hit areas
push()                 -- Push a new frame
pop()                  -- Pops the current frame
waitForTouch([side])   -- Waits for a monitor touch
                          (Advanced monitor)
waitForClick([button]) -- Waits for a button click
                          (Terminal)